===Proper noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

#(''New Testament'') A man, the brother of [[Mary]] and [[Martha]], brought back to life by [[Jesus]] after being in the [[tomb]] for four days.
# (''New Testament'') A [[beggar]] in a [[parable]] told by [[Jesus Christ]].
#{{given name|male|}} A male [[given name]].

